How can I log in to Rally with SSO instead of using my username and password each time?

To set up Single Sign-On (SSO) for Rally, so you donâ€™t need to enter your username and password each time, follow these steps:

Bookmark Your Rally Page
First, navigate to your Rally page and add it to your bookmarks.

Edit the Bookmark
Open your bookmarks, locate the one you just created for Rally, and select the option to edit this bookmark.

Update the URL
Change the bookmarked URL to rally.qq.com.

Access Rally Quickly
Now, whenever you want to access Rally, simply click this bookmark. You'll be automatically logged in via SSO, without needing to enter your username or password.
